Requirements
------------
In order to build Stjerm you need gtk2 and vte.


Installation
------------
Enter the following command to build and install Stjerm (if
necessary as root):
	make install

You can also use some custom options like PREFIX (default is /usr/local),
CFLAGS or LDFLAGS.
Example:
	PREFIX=/usr CFLAGS="-O3 -march=i686" make install

Running
------------
Enter this command to run Stjerm:
	stjerm

The default keybiding for opening the terminal is F1.
